      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and practicality, maintained with a high level of care. The exterior finish retains a deep, impressive luster, though a close inspection will reveal the minor stone chips and light surface marks expected of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seating is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, having received regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake service. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining for the seasons ahead. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
